同翻译的小组，用GitHub等进行版本管理等模式。除了教材/专著，也可以翻译论文或其他图书。另外关于原书的版权授权问题，可以由国家出面统筹解决，也可以“仅供研究学习使用，请下载后于24小时内删除”（逃） 这个想法可行吗？有哪些细节可能存在问题？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Im/qIqpbuyJFuEAMaCDYzNTQ5NTExII2t/IMGMAI4KEAwcgk0NTU3MTI5NTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"84 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/106c37b3fac208b6575edd1a050d19cd_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1618976186.6708746","card_id":"Q_455432516","target":{"id":455432516,"title":"减肥期间忍不住想吃猪肉怎么办？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/455432516","type":"question","created":1618813974,"answer_count":81,"follower_count":103,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,658,680,974,11751],"comment_count":2,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"最近下定决心减肥，每天都控制饮食，低脂低碳水的吃，一个多月下来实在受不了了，周末欺骗餐也就吃口牛排，可我实在太想吃红烧肉之类的东西了，请问各位大神减肥期间忍不住想吃猪肉了该怎么办？有没有什么不影响我减肥的健康吃法？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Im/qIqpbuyJFuEAMaCDYzNDg2OTQ2IJbI9IMGMAI4Z0Axcgk0NTU0MzI1MTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb79187b7657c6554535d34058855d3d_720w.jpg?source=ba7200d9"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-04-21 11:36:26"}}